    <settingList>
        <setting>
            <title>New York City; Wonder Girl's Apartment</title>
            <p>Some of the Teen Titans are hanging out. Wonder Girl and Koriand'r are now roomates.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#starfire">Koriand'r</char>
                <char ref="#wgirl">Wonder Girl</char>
                <char ref="#robin">Robin</char>
                <char ref="#kflash">Kid Flash</char>
                <char ref="#bboy">Beast Boy</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>Fearsome Five Meeting</title>
            <p>Doctor Light gathers the members of the Fearsome Five for a meeting after testing Shimmer and Mammoth.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#shimmer">Shimmer</char>
                <char ref="#mammoth">Mammoth</char>
                <char ref="#drlight">Doctor Light</char>
                <char ref="#psimon">Psimon</char>
                <char ref="#gizmo">Gizmo</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>Back to Wonder Girl's Apartment</title>
            <p>Koriand'r is telling the others about her past. Flashback of Tamaran. Flashback of the Citadel; their overloads sent the Gordanians to attack Tamaran, but King Myand'r offered a peace treaty. Raver appears.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#starfire">Koriand'r</char>
                <char ref="#robin">Robin</char>
                <char ref="#wgirl">Wonder Girl</char>
                <char ref="#bboy">Beast Boy</char>
                <char ref="#kflash">Kid Flash</char>
                <char ref="#citadel">Citadel</char>
                <char ref="#kingmya">King Myand'r</char>
                <char ref="#gordianian">Gordianian(s)</char>
                <char ref="#queenlua">Queen Luand'r</char>
                <char ref="#rya">Ryand'r</char>
                <char ref="#raven">Raven</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>Back to the Fearsome Five.</title>
            <p>The Fearsome Five are talking when the Teen Titans appear due to Raven finding the Fearsome Five's location. A fight breaks out and the Fearsome Five escape after Shimmer puts the Teen Titans to sleep. Raven disappears when the Teen Titans are put to sleep.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#drlight">Doctor Light</char>
                <char ref="#psimon">Psimon</char>
                <char ref="#gizmo">Gizmo</char>
                <char ref="#shimmer">Shimmer</char>
                <char ref="#mammoth">Mammoth</char>
                <char ref="#robin">Robin</char>
                <char ref="#raven">Raven</char>
                <char ref="#starfire">Koriand'r</char>
                <char ref="#bboy">Beast Boy</char>
                <char ref="#kflash">Kid Flash</char>
                <char ref="#wgirl">Wonder Girl</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>Somewhere (location unknown)</title>
            <p>Raven demands answers from Trigon. He's the reason for the Fearsome Five's creation. She disappears when Trigon tries to strike her.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#raven">Raven</char>
                <char ref="#trigon">Trigon</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>New York City, 44th Street and Eleventh Avenue</title>
            <p>Cyborg is in an apartment with his father, Silas Stone. They are having an argument. Cyborg finds a  mysterious letter.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#cyborg">Victor Stone</char>
                <char ref="#sstone">Silas Stone</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>Titans' Tower</title>
            <p>Beast Boy reveals some of his past. Each Titan received a letter that lead them to Titans' Tower on a small island off Manhattan in the East River. They don't know who sent the letter or who built the tower. Raven reappears. She tells the Titans about her visage; images of Trigon, Goronn and the Justice League. It changed from Trigon to the Fearsome Five which is how Raven knew of the warning.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#bboy">Beast Boy</char>
                <char ref="#cyborg">Victor Stone</char>
                <char ref="#robin">Robin</char>
                <char ref="#starfire">Koriand'r</char>
                <char ref="#wgirl">Wonder Girl</char>
                <char ref="#kflash">Kid Flash</char>
                <char ref="#raven">Raven</char>
                <char ref="#goronn">Goronn</char>
                <char ref="#hman">Hawkman</char>
                <char ref="#batman">Batman</char>
                <char ref="#wwoman">Wonder Woman</char>
                <char ref="#glantern">Green Lantern</char>
                <char ref="#zatan">Zatanna</char>
                <char ref="#atom">Atom</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>The New Jersey Palisades Overlooking Uptown Manhattan</title>
            <p>Doctor Light tells the Fearsome Five his plan to kill the Justice League. Psimon shots Doctor Light revealing that he has a mission from Trigon to take down the Titans. He was the one who sent the message to Raven and he sends another to the Titans calling them to fight.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#drlight">Doctor Light</char>
                <char ref="#psimon">Psimon</char>
                <char ref="#shimmer">Shimmer</char>
                <char ref="#mammoth">Mammoth</char>
                <char ref="#gizmo">Gizmo</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>Titans' Tower</title>
            <p>They receive Psimon and decide that they're going to go fight. Raven and Kid Flash stay behind because they think it's a bad idea.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#robin">Robin</char>
                <char ref="#cyborg">Victor Stone</char>
                <char ref="#bboy">Beast Boy</char>
                <char ref="#wgirl">Wonder Girl</char>
                <char ref="#starfire">Koriand'r</char>
                <char ref="#raven">Raven</char>
                <char ref="#kflash">Kid Flash</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>The New Jersey Palisades Overlooking Uptown Manhattan</title>
            <p>The Titans go to fight but it turns into an ambush.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#robin">Robin</char>
                <char ref="#cyborg">Victor Stone</char>
                <char ref="#bboy">Beast Boy</char>
                <char ref="#wgirl">Wonder Girl</char>
                <char ref="#starfire">Koriand'r</char>
                <char ref="#drlight">Doctor Light</char>
                <char ref="#psimon">Psimon</char>
                <char ref="#shimmer">Shimmer</char>
                <char ref="#mammoth">Mammoth</char>
                <char ref="#gizmo">Gizmo</char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>Titans' Tower</title>
            <p>Raven sees that all the Titans except Beast Boy and Koriand'r are unconscious. Kid Flash and Raven decide to join the fight.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#raven"></char>
            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>The New Jersey Palisades Overlooking Uptown Manhattan</title>
            <p>Kid Flash joins the fight, but Mammoth knocks him out. The Titans have been defeated and Raven decides to go to the Justice League.</p>
            <charsPresent>
                <char ref="#robin">Robin</char>
                <char ref="#cyborg">Victor Stone</char>
                <char ref="#bboy">Beast Boy</char>
                <char ref="#wgirl">Wonder Girl</char>
